item.title: Who am I?
item.description: Hello dear friend! Welcome to my new blog. I am 28 year old software developer (Golang developer) from Kazakhstan. Here I will post my updates on Go, Competitive Programming, Security, and other interesting IT things that I will explore on my engineering path.
